 The 2nd Amendment was influenced by the English Bill of Rights to confer an individual right to bear arms. Oral arguments in DC vs. Heller. March 19th, 2008 - "JUSTICE KENNEDY: You think Madison was guided by the experience and the expressions of the right in English law, including the Bill of Rights of 1689?
